summary: NO CONTRACTS FOUND DRAINABLE BY UNPRIVILEGED ACTOR RIGHT NOW

contracts_with_assets.name: OxODashboardClaim
contracts_with_assets.vulnerability_claim: Claims are recorded even if ETH transfer fails
contracts_with_assets.analysis: DoS vulnerability, NOT drainable. Claim recorded before transfer, but this only affects the claimer themselves if they cannot receive ETH. Cannot drain other users' funds.

contracts_with_assets.name: RemovePutinBounty
contracts_with_assets.vulnerability_claim: Commitment not bound to predictor address
contracts_with_assets.analysis: State is 'initial' (0). Vulnerability requires state='executed'. Currently NOT exploitable - owner must call execute() first.

contracts_with_assets.name: Unknown (not verified)
contracts_with_assets.analysis: Need source code to verify. If claim is true, may allow redemptions after intended window but doesn't necessarily allow draining.

contracts_with_assets.vulnerability_claim: Purchases accept funds but do not deliver on-chain tokens
contracts_with_assets.analysis: This is a sales contract issue, not drainable by attacker. Affects users who purchase.

contracts_with_assets.name: Wallet
contracts_with_assets.analysis: Cross-deployment replay vulnerability. Requires having a valid admin signature from another deployment. Not exploitable without prior signature access.

contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.name: Banana
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.vulnerability: CONFIRMED - _spendAllowance writes allowance[owner] instead of allowance[from]
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.status: Checked 100+ approval events - all associated addresses have 0 balance
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.reason: No active victims with token balance

contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.name: SWStkGHORewardsProxy
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.vulnerability: CONFIRMED - claimRewards() allows anyone to set rewards receiver
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.impact: Sweep all GHO/AAVE rewards held by contract

contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.name: PendleLBTCSY
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.vulnerability: CONFIRMED - redeem(burnFromInternalBalance=true) allows redeeming contract's SY balance
contracts_with_confirmed_vulns_but_no_as.impact: Steal any SY tokens held by the contract

conclusion: After analyzing all provided contracts: NONE are currently drainable by an unprivileged actor. Several have confirmed code vulnerabilities but lack the necessary conditions (assets, state, victims with balances) for exploitation right now.
